Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三忍攻防战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛤蟆龙 快离开这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话 快跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万蛇 大蛇丸 蛞蝓 还有纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是久未谋面的面孔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开同学会吗 自来也
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没召唤你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一来就讲些无聊的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该把多年的老账算算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要在这里干掉大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次别召唤我做这种无聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当心我吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说 万蛇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事后一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人问你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随便跟我说话 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事后给我准备一百个活人作祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是它的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果让万蛇\N知道大蛇丸大人不能使用忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万蛇一定会倒戈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但此刻召唤万蛇真是场危险的赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛞蝓 把那小子带到静音那儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静音大人 这孩子就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外这里马上就有一场死斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和我的分身找个地方躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是纲手大人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我把你变成蛤蟆干啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正想要个蛇皮钱包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸 你作恶多端
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不再是同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人汗毛直竖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后 我们不再并称三忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌齿黏酸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住一只
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛞蝓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手 闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文太 用油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.蛤蟆油炎弹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这两下子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空壳 被它蜕皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文太 当心地下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是三忍 一次对付两个很吃力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样勒死你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查克拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你在战斗中死不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么勒下去一定会死吧 纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说几分钟了 就连几秒钟也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能赌一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 差不多该做个了断了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来已经到达极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挨了我这么多下还安然无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不过如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少狂妄了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别停 继续揍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我…豁出性命的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得陪我玩到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打来打去总觉得有些不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这异样的感觉到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被她的蛮力直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分出胜负了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我弄成这样 想让我吃了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴被开了个洞 看来是吃不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记住 别再让我碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你不帮我疗伤 我也有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活这双手的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶一定会被摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我们到时还能再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手 自来也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像用什么办法把别人的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才对战的时候总感觉和以前不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正长生不老的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将永世不灭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肋骨和脚都受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍术的副作用开始生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是老样子逢赌必输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为火影是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你一周的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能限期学会那招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就承认你能成为火影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并把这条项链送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没在说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧着吧 像这种忍术 只要三天就能学会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男子汉可别食言哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是创造了这个木叶的初代火影的孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好 男子汉可别食言哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要像爷爷那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朝一日也要成为火影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常喜欢村子里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想保护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为保护大家而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为火影是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能接受这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副作用差不多生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:17:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要稍微休息一下就能变年轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先去镇上休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等鸣人醒了之后就回木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始 我不是纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要称呼我为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五代火影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手婆婆从今天起就是第五代火影了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 好像挺不服气的嘛 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 和三代爷爷比起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脾气坏 个性倔 乱花钱 又阴险又笨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于她能否胜任 我可非常担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…纲手大人 您要不要来点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是个五十岁的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是使了什么变身术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是火影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺骗大家可不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出去聊聊吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么感觉又回到起点了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说 我也是第五代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付一个小鬼是不会当真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一根手指足以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别老当我是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是我 总有一天也会当上火影的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要弹我的额头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要成为一个出色的男子汉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且要成为一名伟大的火影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 该回木叶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我们还没吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想傻笑蒙混啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绳树 断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承了你们梦想的那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算到了 温泉村
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好色仙人流着鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手婆婆好像也去了什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我偶尔也放松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什么人弄乱了我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.61,0:22:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要将他揪出来痛揍一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人的奇异温泉之旅
